    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Puerto Rico Hospital Medicare Reimbursement Equity Act of 2015</b></p> <p> Amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to revise the formula for the Medicare inpatient hospital services payment rate for Puerto Rico hospitals to: (1) reduce the applicable Puerto Rico percentage from 25% to zero, and (2) increase the applicable federal percentage from 75% to 100%.</p>]]></text>
